"""
    Test that various wrapping methods and settings can be used to correctly
    wrap key data.
    """
engine = crypto.CryptographyEngine()
result = engine.wrap_key(wrapping_parameters.get('key_material'),
    wrapping_parameters.get('wrapping_method'), wrapping_parameters.get(
    'key_wrap_algorithm'), wrapping_parameters.get('encryption_key'))
assert wrapping_parameters.get('wrapped_data') == result
